            <title>[LU-199] can&apos;t clear ext4 journal stats</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-199</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On the MDS you can easily gather mdt journal stats by a read to /proc/fs/jb2/&amp;lt;mtd dev id&amp;gt;/info. This file is read only so it is impossible to clear the values to make data analysis easier.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
